{"body": "Regulation 7 (determination of the maximum rate at which a person or persons may be entitled to child tax credit) of the Child Tax Credit Regulations 2002 is amended as follows\u2014\nin paragraph (4)(c) and 4(f) for \u201c\u00a33,235\u201d substitute \u201c\u00a33,455\u201d; and\nin paragraph (5)\u2014\nin sub-paragraph (a) for \u201c\u00a33,905\u201d substitute \u201c\u00a34,170\u201d; and\nin sub-paragraph (b) for \u201c\u00a35,480\u201d substitute \u201c\u00a35,850\u201d.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2024/247 reg. 3", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2024/247/3", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2024-04-06", "heading": "Regulation 3", "id": "6fb94045-e12a-5d81-8a29-7706fa8599d5", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "247", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "3", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2024"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2024/247 reg. 3", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": [], "references_to": ["uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247", "uksi/2024/247"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 3, "parent_citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2024/247", "parent_id": "5a52727c-629f-57f6-9be1-99f6348c2bc8", "source_as_of": "2024-04-06", "source_document_id": "uksi/2024/247", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2024/247/regulation/3/made", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-06-05-uk-tax-credits-uprating-2024-reg3/uksi/2024/247/regulation-3.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2024/247/regulation/3/made", "version": "2026-06-05-uk-tax-credits-uprating-2024-reg3"}
